title: Childhood
creator: Leo Tolstoy
description: LibriVox recording of Childhood (Детство [Detstvo]) by Leo Tolstoy. Read in Russian by Yakovlev Valery and Yakovleva Evgeniya Childhood (Детство [Detstvo]; 1852) is the first novel in Leo Tolstoy's autobiographical trilogy. They are the works that launched his writing career. These books earned him instant acclaim. This book describes the major physiological decisions of boyhood that all boys experience.
